                     <interp inst="t17831210-106-person1136" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , her mark."</p>
               <p>"The examination of 
               <persName id="t17831210-106-person1137">
                  Sarah
                   Thurlin
               <interp inst="t17831210-106-person1137" type="surname" value="Thurlin"></interp>
